-live-at-glastonbury-2022-setlist-photos-review-3255717">2022 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节成为头条新闻</a>以来的首场演出。预计他将于 2023 年 10 月开始在澳大利亚举行一系列演出。</p><p>这位前披头士成员上次巡演澳大利亚是在 2017 年。他曾于 1964 年随披头士乐队巡演澳大利亚，并于 1975 年和 1993 年随 Wings 巡演。</p><p>在 Macca 的其他新闻中，这位音乐家最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/steven-spielberg-and-paul-mccartney-attend-oppenheimer-screening-together-3473894">与史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格一起观看了克里斯托弗·诺兰的<em>《奥本海默》</em>的放映</a>。周一（7 月 24 日），两人被发现出现在纽约暑假热点汉普顿的一家电影院外。</p><p>网络游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/destiny-2-fans-think-paul-mccartney-is-coming-back-for-a-new-soundtrack-3473012"><em>《命运 2》</em>的粉丝一直猜测 Macca 可能是游戏回归的原声带的一部分</a>。</p><p> <em>《命运 2》</em>的编曲家 Ella Rae Feingold 最近在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/instagram">Instagram</a>帐户上分享了一张<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvFZz9EueAV/?img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乐谱照片</a>，遮盖了参与创作的人员的名字，但她留下了“P.麦卡特尼”可见。</p><p>保罗<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-teases-major-international-tour-got-to-get-you-into-my-life-3475705">·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 调侃大型国际巡演的帖子：“让你进入我的生活”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
鲍勃·格尔多夫 (Bob Geldof) 记得西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O'Connor) 去世前几周收到的短信https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-remembers-text-messages-received-from-sinead-oconnor-weeks-before-her-death-3475761?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bob-格尔多夫记得她去世前几周从西尼德·奥康纳那里收到的短信Liberty DunworthMon, 31 Jul 2023 15:06:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3475761 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1993 年 9 月 1 日，The Boomtown Rats 乐队的 Bob Geldof 在 Let&#39;s Rock Southampton Festival 2023 上表演，Sinead O&#39;Connor 在伊利诺伊州芝加哥舞台上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他将一些信息描述为“充满绝望、绝望和悲伤”</p><p>鲍勃<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-remembers-text-messages-received-from-sinead-oconnor-weeks-before-her-death-3475761">·格尔多夫 (Bob Geldof) 回忆西尼德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor) 去世前几周收到的短信的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="1993 年 9 月 1 日，The Boomtown Rats 乐队的 Bob Geldof 在 Let&#39;s Rock Southampton Festival 2023 上表演，Sinead O&#39;Connor 在伊利诺伊州芝加哥舞台上表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Bob-Geldof-Sinead-OConnor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-geldof">鲍勃·格尔多夫 (Bob Geldof)</a>回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinead O&#39;Connor)</a>去世前几周在最近的一场演出中与她交谈的情景。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手兼作曲家和活动家在爱尔兰 Cavan Calling 音乐节的舞台上回忆起他与这位音乐家的长期友谊。在这里，他回顾了与她和她的家人在同一条道路上成长的经历，以及对她在公众视野中的勇气的钦佩。</p><p> “她对每个人来说都很重要。她对我们来说意义重大。”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-boomtown-rats">这位 Boomtown Rats</a>歌手开始说道。 “Sinead 住在同一条街上，距离路大约 75 码。我认识她和她的哥哥约瑟夫，伟大的小说家。我们过去常常共用 7A 公交车站去上学……所以我和奥康纳斯一家一起长大，他们很棒，而她是一名手枪。</p><p> “她是无情的。她的声音是我们从未听过的——如此纯净。作为一位伟大的艺术家，那个声音完全代表了她的灵魂和精神，每当我们听到这个声音时，我们都会永远和这位伟大的女人在一起。”</p><p>他继续说道，还谈到了她一生所经历的“可怕的孤独”和“绝望”，并承认最近几周他收到了她的短信——回忆起她所经历的高潮和低谷。 。</p><p> “正如你们都知道的那样，除了继续下去，没有其他选择。很多很多时候，西尼德都充满了可怕的孤独和可怕的绝望，”他解释道。 “她是我的一个非常好的朋友。几周前我们还在讨论。她的一些文字充满了绝望、绝望和悲伤，有些则充满了欣喜若狂的快乐。她本来就是这样的。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="2023 年 7 月 30 日" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vNCssQGRSN4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="新兴城市之鼠还记得西妮德·奥康纳和加里·罗伯茨：第四年级的戴夫和玛丽" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ieZ4HY54X-E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在他感人至深的悼念活动即将结束时——他穿着一件正面印有她照片的 T 恤——他还赞扬了她在 1992 年<em>《周六夜现场》</em>中的勇敢表现。</p><p>这段现在臭名昭著的片段显示，奥康纳以无伴奏合唱形式翻唱了鲍勃·马利的歌曲《战争》，随后撕碎了一张教皇约翰·保罗二世在说出“邪恶”一词时的照片，并将碎片扔向镜头，说道“与真正的敌人作战”。该表演是为了抗议教堂中对儿童的性虐待，并导致她被禁止参加演出。</p><p> “She tore up the picture of the Pope because she saw me tear up the picture of John Travolta on <em>Top Of The Pops</em> ,” he said. “It was a little more extreme than tearing up fucking disco. Tearing up the Vatican is a whole other thing but more correct actually. I should have done it.” </p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v17.0" nonce="weNRKzR0"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/theboomtownrats/posts/pfbid0Lvdxbk1sMxHm9EEqiLBXgVNqJ84KbAZKnf2p6iRgMD1NwLKRw8fLheLgx5169EKPl?locale=en_GB" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100044445969251/posts/839135664244625/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p> https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vNCssQGRSN4VIDEO FROM JULIE KORETZ</p><p> Posted by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/theboomtownrats">The Boomtown Rats</a> on <a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100044445969251/posts/839135664244625/">Sunday, July 30, 2023</a></p></blockquote></div><p> The iconic Irish singer and activist <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">died at the age of 56</a> last week, after being <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-found-unresponsive-at-home-police-say-3474196">found unresponsive in her London home</a> .她被宣布当场死亡。</p><p> The news came one year after the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-pays-tribute-to-17-year-old-son-following-his-death-3132870">death of her son Shane, who died by suicide</a> . Currently, no cause of death for the singer has been announced, although the police have confirmed that the circumstances are not being treated as suspicious.</p><p> Tributes quickly poured in from across the music industry from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-t">Ice-T</a> and many more.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-and-brandi-carlile-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474214">P!nk and Brandi Carlile soon paid live tribute to the singer</a> , covering &#39;Nothing Compares 2 U&#39; at a recent show. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fall-out-boy-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474325">Fall Out Boy also covered the song at a recent gig</a> , while <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighers-and-alanis-morissette-honour-sinead-oconnor-with-mandinka-cover-3475206">Foo Fighters and Alanis Morissette performed &#39;Mandinka&#39;</a> at a recent festival.</p><p> Additionally, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sinead-oconnor-fans-gather-to-sing-nothing-compares-2-u-at-dublin-tribute-3475498">fans gathered in Dublin this weekend and to sing her cover of the Prince song</a> , while Ruth Coppinger, an activist and former Irish parliamentarian, paid tribute to the late singer at the gathering, describing her as an “exceptional and unique voice that could be both a whisper or a scream in one line”.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bob-geldof-remembers-text-messages-received-from-sinead-oconnor-weeks-before-her-death-3475761">Bob Geldof remembers text messages received from Sinead O&#39;Connor weeks before her death</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
